                                How Democracies Die</a>                            </p>
                            <div class="attribution text-xs mb-0">by Steven Levitsky and Daniel Ziblatt</div>
                            <div class="details text-label mb-0 color-gray">Broadway, 302 pp., $15.00 (paper)</div>
                        </article>
