                                                                    <a href="https://www.bookshop.org/a/312/9780525574460" target="_blank" class="color-black hover-text-ny-red">
                                The Road to Unfreedom: Russia, Europe, America</a>                            </p>
                            <div class="attribution text-xs mb-0">by Timothy Snyder</div>
